OL,6,FThe sustainable mobility company EVie
OL,7,Fhas announced it has temporarily
OL,8,Fsuspended its fleet of electric bikes
OL,9,Fin .
OL,11,FThe company said it's because its
OL,12,Fcurrent insurance provider had
OL,13,F"unexpectedly" withdrawn from the
OL,14,FJersey market with "unsatisfactorily
OL,15,Fabrupt notice".JAll bikes were
OL,16,Fautomatically 'turned off' at midnight
OL,17,Fon Saturday 2 March and they'll be
OL,18,Fcollected from around the island soon.
