OL,6,F"This unsatisfactorily abrupt notice,
OL,7,Famidst the currently turbulent
OL,8,Finsurance market in the Channel
OL,9,FIslands, has made it impossible to
OL,10,Fcontinue to offer our dockless bike
OL,11,Fwithout interruption."
